## Pipeline Orchestration

```python
from core_engine.processing.pipeline_orchestrator import ProcessingPipelineOrchestrator

pipeline = ProcessingPipelineOrchestrator(config)

# Process ONCE, share with all strategies
enriched_data = await pipeline.process_market_data(
    symbols=['AAPL', 'TSLA'],
    start_time=datetime(2024, 1, 1),
    end_time=datetime(2024, 12, 31)
)

# enriched_data[symbol] contains: raw_data, indicators, features, signals
```

